    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-05-22T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-05-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="444" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d444">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to
                                    Mr. <persName type="to">Blount</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 2.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-05-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 22,
                                    1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I inclose herewith, the letter of the
                                President recalling Mr. John L. Stevens, your predecessor in the
                                mission to the Hawaiian Islands, with an office copy of the
                                same.</p>
                <p>Mr. Stevens, having taken his departure from Honolulu, you will, at
                                the same time you ask an audience for the purpose of presenting your
                                letters of credence, request the privilege of delivering Mr.
                                Steven’s letters of recall in view of his departure before they
                                could reach him.</p>
                <p>I am, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. Q.
                                Gresham.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
